song_name: Youre The One As Long As We Beat The English

version_description: Alter Bridge - Broken Wings with Capo 1.
Different chords, adding strum rhythm too.

These are the chords for My Champion by Alter Bridge. The song is in standard tuning but has a capo on the 1st fret to make things easier (the chords I've written out are relative to a capo on the 1st fret). In terms of the arrangement/strumming pattern, I've taken inspiration from this acoustic version Myles did (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j4m7Wp6jnk8). The only chords I'm unsure about are the ones for the bridge so please feel free to edit them if you find something that fits better but bear in mind this tab is suppose to be simplistic and easy enough for beginners to play.
This version have chords less simple and more completes.
